sentences.en: No. I 've promised to see Betty this Friday evening.

sentences.en: No one knows the Los Angeles area better than Betty.
sentences.vi: Không ai biết rõ khu Los Angeles hơn Betty.

sentences.en: Betty and Sue are going to New York.
sentences.vi: Betty and sue đang đi tới new york.

sentences.en: Hurricane Betty is now approaching the coast of Florida.
sentences.vi: Trận cuồng phong Betty bây giờ đang tiến tới bờ biển Florida.
